metadata.name: 30-minute Consulting with Farokh
metadata.description:
The lucky owner of this reward will be able to book one (1) 30-minute consultation call with Farokh via Zoom.

How to Redeem:  
1. This NFT reward is redeemable for up to 1 year from mint date (March 7th, 2024).  
2. Holder must be a member of our Rewards Program (https://rug.fm/rewards).  
3. Send an email to info@rug.fm for further instructions.

NOTE: This is an opportunity to ask Farokh anything or share any information you want with him. It is not an automatic or implied endorsement from him whether publicly or privately of your project or initiative.
